6
00:04:30,637 --> 00:04:33,105
U svakom slucaju, ja sam, uh...
Ja sam sve spremio gore.

7
00:04:33,206 --> 00:04:35,640
Tvoja majka je gore.
O cemu je knjiga?

8
00:04:35,742 --> 00:04:38,336
- Oh, Dejvid Koperfild.
- Bices srecan ako budes imao vremena za citanje.

9
00:04:38,444 --> 00:04:40,344
Ja nikada nisam imao.

10
00:04:41,514 --> 00:04:44,176
- Je li sve poneo?
- Naravno, i ne treba mu puno.

11
00:04:44,284 --> 00:04:47,276
- Sta si mislio time, "i ne treba mu puno"?
- Pa, oni ce mu dati sve sto treba-

12
00:04:47,387 --> 00:04:49,287
odecu, namirnice, i tako to.

13
00:04:49,389 --> 00:04:51,755
Njemu treba ono sto sam mu ja dala.

14
00:04:51,858 --> 00:04:55,055
Vreme je za autobus, momce.
Ne zelis da propustis taj voz.

15
00:05:02,402 --> 00:05:05,462
- Cao, Mama.
- Srecno, Sine.

16
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:50,038
Podjimo.

17
00:06:53,279 --> 00:06:56,806
Pomeri se, sine.
Povuci se. Povuci se.

18
00:06:56,916 --> 00:07:00,044
- Iznesite! Iznesite!
- Naslonite na zid.

19
00:07:43,729 --> 00:07:45,720
Ima nekoga gore.

20
00:07:57,310 --> 00:08:00,746
- Idemo.
- Povucite ta creva! Nazad! Nazad!

21
00:08:00,847 --> 00:08:04,112
U redu, cuvajte se!
Rusi se! Rusi se!

22
00:08:14,660 --> 00:08:17,527
Zao mi je, momce. Upravo si ga propustio.

23
00:08:36,215 --> 00:08:39,082
Idi i naspavaj se malo.
Ja cu zavrsiti ovde.

24
00:09:04,677 --> 00:09:08,044
Okupili smo se ovde,
draga i voljena braco po Hristu...

25
00:09:08,147 --> 00:09:10,342
da ovo dete bude ponovo rodjeno...

26
00:09:10,449 --> 00:09:13,816
i primljeno u porodicu 
Hristove crkve...

27
00:09:13,920 --> 00:09:17,583
zahvalimo svemogucem Bogu
za ove blagodeti...

28
00:09:17,690 --> 00:09:21,626
i da, svi zajedno,
pomolimo se Bogu za njega...

29
00:09:21,727 --> 00:09:25,288
da ovo dete do kraja svog zivota bude 
prosvetljno prema ovom novom pocetku.

30
00:09:43,683 --> 00:09:47,813
Jesi li ti za kamp?
Hej, ti!

31
00:09:47,920 --> 00:09:51,253
- Jesi li ti za kamp?
- Jesam.

32
00:09:51,357 --> 00:09:54,656
Malo si zakasnio, sinko.
Ostali su stigli sinoc.

33
00:09:54,760 --> 00:09:56,421
Znam.

34
00:09:56,529 --> 00:09:58,690
Uhvatilo te bombardovanje, eh?

35
00:09:58,798 --> 00:10:00,823
- Da.
- Oh, pa, nema veze, sinko.

36
00:10:00,933 --> 00:10:05,165
Moraces da pesacis.
Nema puno milja.

37
00:11:05,498 --> 00:11:08,194
Spusti kofer dole.

38
00:11:08,300 --> 00:11:10,598
- Ime?
- Tomas Bedous.

39
00:11:10,703 --> 00:11:12,330
Gospodine.

40
00:11:12,438 --> 00:11:14,929
- Tomas Bedous, gospodine.
- Kasnis.

41
00:11:17,810 --> 00:11:20,802
I... stoj!

42
00:11:28,688 --> 00:11:31,714
I... stoj!

43
00:11:35,428 --> 00:11:37,328
Ko si ti?

44
00:11:38,531 --> 00:11:41,796
- Tomas Bedous, gospodine.
- Da li ti licim na oficira?

45
00:11:41,901 --> 00:11:43,869
- Napred, mars!
- Ne, gospodine.

46
00:11:43,969 --> 00:11:46,597
Ne zovi me "gospodine" onda.

47
00:11:46,706 --> 00:11:49,266
Ko ti je dozvolio da upadnes ovde?

48
00:11:49,375 --> 00:11:51,343
- Da sta?
- Da udjes ovde.

49
00:11:51,444 --> 00:11:54,470
Da udjes u sobu.
Da otvoris vrata i da izvedes ulazak.

50
00:11:55,881 --> 00:11:59,009
- Niko.
- Uradi to onda kako treba.

51
00:11:59,118 --> 00:12:01,678
Izadji napolje, kucaj.

52
00:12:01,787 --> 00:12:04,779
I kad ja kazem "da,"
udji i kazi, "Trazim dozvolu za ulaz."

53
00:12:06,425 --> 00:12:08,552
Hajde.

54
00:12:13,299 --> 00:12:15,824
Bedous.

55
00:12:15,935 --> 00:12:18,597
Tvoj kofer... uzmi ga.

56
00:12:32,051 --> 00:12:33,951
Da?

57
00:12:37,757 --> 00:12:41,454
- Ko si ti?
- Bedous. Trazim dozvolu za ulaz.

58
00:12:41,560 --> 00:12:44,358
Udji, Redove Bedous.

59
00:12:44,463 --> 00:12:47,330
Mozes uzeti onaj.

60
00:12:56,575 --> 00:12:58,475
Ostavi to.

61
00:12:58,577 --> 00:13:01,944
Vec dovoljno kasnis.
Sledece po redu je sisanje.

62
00:13:02,047 --> 00:13:05,175
Naci ces berbernicu
odmah pored kancelarije cete.

63
00:13:05,284 --> 00:13:07,752
- Sledeci!
- Stani mirno. Stani mirno.

64
00:13:07,853 --> 00:13:10,447
Stani mirno.. Sledeci.

65
00:13:10,556 --> 00:13:12,922
Sledeci. Ime?

66
00:13:13,025 --> 00:13:15,050
- Bedous, gospodine.
- Malo si mrsav, zar ne?

67
00:13:15,161 --> 00:13:17,061
Da, gospodine.

68
00:13:18,197 --> 00:13:20,097
- Imas li kasalj?
- Ne, gospodine.

69
00:13:20,199 --> 00:13:22,724
- U redu. Obuci se tamo.
- Sledeci.

70
00:13:25,638 --> 00:13:28,505
- Hocete li me ubosti time?
- Ruku, molim.

71
00:13:34,947 --> 00:13:37,814
Osecas li se bolje?

72
00:13:37,917 --> 00:13:40,112
Ne volim igle.

73
00:13:40,219 --> 00:13:43,655
Je li to sve?
Ja ne volim celu smrdljivu vojsku.

74
00:13:43,756 --> 00:13:47,783
Svi regruti, poredjajte se pored vrata.
Postrojite se. Pokret!

75
00:13:47,893 --> 00:13:51,090
Dobro!
Abrahams, Arlot, Bedous!

76
00:13:51,197 --> 00:13:54,496
Malkolm, Partridz Silver, Jang.

77
00:13:54,600 --> 00:13:56,932
Dobro. Da vas vidim.

78
00:14:12,084 --> 00:14:14,416
Mozes li mi reci sta imas tu?

79
00:14:15,921 --> 00:14:19,220
Jedan par gaca, P.T.
Jedan par gaca, kruzne.

80
00:14:19,325 --> 00:14:21,919
Jedna balaklava.
Jedan par tregera. Jedan par cizama.

81
00:14:22,027 --> 00:14:24,154
Veliki kaput, carape, prsluci, dokolenice.

82
00:14:24,263 --> 00:14:26,595
Tvrda tkanina,
malo i veliko pakovanje.

83
00:14:26,699 --> 00:14:28,599
Ratnicka odora, gas maska.

84
00:14:30,202 --> 00:14:33,638
Porcija, cutura,
noz, viljuska i kasika.

85
00:14:35,040 --> 00:14:37,600
Nesto jos osim toga?

86
00:14:37,710 --> 00:14:39,678
Mislim da ne.

87
00:14:41,780 --> 00:14:43,805
Sta je to?

88
00:14:43,916 --> 00:14:45,907
To je kanap za ciscenje puske.

89
00:14:46,018 --> 00:14:47,918
Ucis.

90
00:14:50,155 --> 00:14:52,055
U redu, svi vi!

91
00:14:52,157 --> 00:14:55,593
Ima da odrzavate ovaj pod tako blistavim
da me zaslepi, i ima da pocnete upravo sad!

92
00:14:55,694 --> 00:14:58,288
Hajde da odmah rascistimo dve stvari!

93
00:14:58,397 --> 00:15:02,857
Prva stvar:
Komanda, "Voljno."

94
00:15:02,968 --> 00:15:05,596
Necete se pokretati ni malo...

95
00:15:05,704 --> 00:15:08,298
dok ne izgovorim tu komandu!

96
00:15:08,407 --> 00:15:12,173
Necete se vrpoljiti,
okretati ili bilo sta drugo!

97
00:15:12,278 --> 00:15:14,246
- Je li to jasno?
- Da, kaplare!

98
00:15:14,346 --> 00:15:16,780
- Je li to jasno??
- Da, kaplare!

99
00:15:18,083 --> 00:15:21,610
Ustaj! Umivanje! Brijanje! Oblaci se!

100
00:15:21,720 --> 00:15:23,779
Ocistite ovu sobu u baraci,
i to hocu tako da sija!

101
00:15:23,889 --> 00:15:26,050
- Jedan!
- Dva!
- Tri!

102
00:15:26,158 --> 00:15:27,819
- Cetiri!
- Pet!
- Sest!

103
00:15:27,927 --> 00:15:29,554
- Sedam!
- Osam!
- Devet!

104
00:15:29,662 --> 00:15:31,186
- Deset!
- Jedanaest!
- Dvanaest!

105
00:15:31,297 --> 00:15:35,393
Neparni brojevi, jedan korak napred!

106
00:15:35,501 --> 00:15:39,995
Parni brojevi, jedan korak nazad!

107
00:15:40,105 --> 00:15:42,005
- Mars!
- Jedan, dva!

108
00:15:42,107 --> 00:15:44,371
- Jang, koliko ceta ima u jednom bataljonu?
- Cetiri cete.

109
00:15:44,476 --> 00:15:48,003
- Bedous, ime bataljonskog narednika.
- Bataljonski narednik Palmer.

110
00:15:48,113 --> 00:15:51,571
- Tacno! Ima li pitanja?
- Bataljon je osnovan 1685.

111
00:15:52,618 --> 00:15:54,643
- Da.
- Zbog cega?

112
00:15:56,255 --> 00:15:58,553
Mislim, da li je bilo nekog posebnog razloga?

113
00:15:58,657 --> 00:16:00,852
- Sta ti mislis?
- Ne znam.

114
00:16:00,960 --> 00:16:03,360
Da zadivi Francuze!

115
00:16:04,463 --> 00:16:07,296
U redu. Da pogledamo sta ste uradili 
do sada. Stanite pored svojih kreveta!

116
00:16:24,550 --> 00:16:27,178
Dobro! Sada, pocecemo sve 
iz pocetka, hocemo li?

117
00:16:27,286 --> 00:16:29,379
- Broji!
- Jedan, dva, tri! Jedan!

118
00:16:29,488 --> 00:16:32,321
Ne mrdaj! Savrseno ne mrdaj!

119
00:16:32,424 --> 00:16:35,587
Formiraj liniju po tri! Brzo.

120
00:16:35,694 --> 00:16:37,662
Mars! Centar. Pozadi.

121
00:16:37,763 --> 00:16:40,061
Ispred. Centar. Pozadi.

122
00:16:40,165 --> 00:16:42,360
Ispred. Centar. Pozadi.

123
00:16:42,468 --> 00:16:44,663
Ispred. Centar. Pozadi.

124
00:16:44,770 --> 00:16:46,897
Ispred. Centar. Pozadi.

125
00:16:47,006 --> 00:16:49,873
Ispred. Pozadi. I popuni tu.

126
00:16:51,243 --> 00:16:53,143
Dobro!

127
00:16:53,245 --> 00:16:55,145
- Okret!
- Jedan, dva...

128
00:16:55,247 --> 00:16:57,442
Sada se razmaknite! Hajde, brze!

129
00:16:57,549 --> 00:17:01,178
U visini ruku, tvoje desno!
Pogled na desno!

130
00:17:01,286 --> 00:17:03,550
Dizi ruku.

131
00:17:03,655 --> 00:17:06,749
... napred!

132
00:17:14,600 --> 00:17:17,569
- Bedous, zar ne?
- Da, gospodine.

133
00:17:17,669 --> 00:17:20,035
Sta nisi dobro uradio, Bedous?

134
00:17:22,674 --> 00:17:25,643
Izgleda da sam propustio da izbelim 
pojas ispod kopce, gospodine.

135
00:17:25,744 --> 00:17:28,542
- Sredi to sledeci put.
- Da, gospodine.

136
00:17:28,647 --> 00:17:31,616
Na desno! Brzo marsiranje!

137
00:17:31,717 --> 00:17:35,084
Leva, desna! Leva, desna! Sad!

138
00:17:35,187 --> 00:17:37,087
Odred!

139
00:17:38,357 --> 00:17:40,257
- Stoj!
- Leva, jedan, dva!

140
00:17:40,359 --> 00:17:43,556
Sta to, dodjavola, radis, Bedous?
Pomeri se jako nazad!

141
00:17:46,331 --> 00:17:49,095
Uvrci! Uvrci!

142
00:17:49,201 --> 00:17:50,828
Pocepaj ga!

143
00:17:57,876 --> 00:18:01,073
Hajde! Hajde! Drzite ruke gore!

144
00:18:01,180 --> 00:18:04,081
- Jebem mu, prodji izmedju--
- Vhoa!

145
00:18:04,183 --> 00:18:07,778
Ne gledaj dole. Ne gledaj dole!
Prokleta budalo!

146
00:18:07,886 --> 00:18:11,788
Hajde! Hajde!
Plasite se da ne pokvasite noge?

147
00:18:13,592 --> 00:18:17,119
Pazite da vam te puske ostanu suve!

148
00:18:17,229 --> 00:18:20,027
Penji se uz te proklete merdevine!

149
00:18:23,769 --> 00:18:27,227
Hajde! Sta mislis da je ovo, izlet?

150
00:18:29,074 --> 00:18:31,634
Hajde!
Ustaj, ti blesavi stvore!

151
00:18:35,447 --> 00:18:38,507
Hajde! Jos niste zavrsili!

152
00:18:55,033 --> 00:18:56,933
Jebem ti. Moram da zapalim.

153
00:18:57,970 --> 00:18:59,870
Oni su ispred.

154
00:18:59,972 --> 00:19:02,998
Pa, ti produzi.
Ja cu da zastanem da zapalim.

155
00:19:23,162 --> 00:19:26,154
- Mrzim ovaj rat.
- Preboleces.

156
00:19:29,001 --> 00:19:32,596
Ne, nije to u pitanju.
Moja devojka.

157
00:19:34,206 --> 00:19:36,436
Verili smo se, znas, i onda...

158
00:19:38,210 --> 00:19:41,338
i kada su me mobilisali,
pa...

159
00:19:41,446 --> 00:19:43,414
njen stari mi nije
dozvolio da je ozenim.

160
00:19:44,683 --> 00:19:46,878
Nek ide bestraga.

161
00:19:46,985 --> 00:19:50,352
Rekao je da treba da 
sacekamo dok ne dobijemo rat.

162
00:19:50,455 --> 00:19:52,355
Kopile.

163
00:19:53,792 --> 00:19:57,922
Dozvolio bi da mu Svabe tucaju zenu
cim bi mu pokucali na vrata.

164
00:20:09,875 --> 00:20:11,843
Zeleo sam da letim.

165
00:20:13,745 --> 00:20:15,645
Nisam prosao lekarski.

166
00:20:17,216 --> 00:20:19,116
Nisam znao za to.

167
00:20:22,888 --> 00:20:25,857
- Ko tebe ceka kod kuce, Tomi?
- Koga ja imam?

168
00:20:27,726 --> 00:20:30,559
Pa, tu su mama i tata, predpostavljam.

169
00:20:30,662 --> 00:20:32,630
I Tina.

170
00:20:33,899 --> 00:20:35,867
Dobro za tebe, druze.

171
00:20:35,968 --> 00:20:37,868
Pusti me da pogadjam.

172
00:20:37,970 --> 00:20:41,337
Ona ima smedju kosu, braon oci...

173
00:20:41,440 --> 00:20:44,273
belu kozu, lepe sise, tacno?

174
00:20:45,911 --> 00:20:47,879
Tina je koker spanijel.

175
00:20:50,816 --> 00:20:53,341
- Ona je divan pas.
- Kucka?

176
00:20:53,452 --> 00:20:55,977
Da. Kucka.

177
00:21:06,164 --> 00:21:08,792
Sta ces raditi kada se sve ovo zavrsi?

178
00:21:11,103 --> 00:21:13,003
Oh, ne znam.

179
00:21:14,840 --> 00:21:16,740
Ja imam planove.

180
00:21:17,809 --> 00:21:19,709
Garaza, druze.

181
00:21:19,811 --> 00:21:23,474
Kupicu garazu negde ovde u blizini
u bacicu se na posao secenja metala.

182
00:21:23,582 --> 00:21:26,278
- Sta kazes na to da se udruzis sa mnom, Tom?
- Hej. Trebalo bi da krenemo.

183
00:21:33,692 --> 00:21:35,887
Izlazis sutra sa mnom i sa momcima?

184
00:21:35,994 --> 00:21:38,861
Proslavljamo... kraj obuke.

185
00:21:38,964 --> 00:21:42,661
Pab je pun poslepodne,
uvece je prava ludnica.

186
00:21:42,768 --> 00:21:44,736
Dobro. Dobro. vazi.

187
00:21:46,471 --> 00:21:48,405
O cemu je film?

188
00:21:48,507 --> 00:21:51,965
Zaboravi slike, druze.
U pitanju je zena.

189
00:21:52,077 --> 00:21:56,377
Sesces pored dobrog komada u poslednjim redovima,
i otici cete pre nego sto se i pojavi naslov filma.

190
00:21:58,417 --> 00:22:00,510
Oh, za Bozje zdravlje.

191
00:22:01,620 --> 00:22:04,714
- Imaju bar 10 minuta prednosti.
- Mislis?

192
00:22:04,823 --> 00:22:07,018
Nema prokletog provoda za nas veceras.

193
00:22:09,628 --> 00:22:12,256
- Idem dole.
- Sta, dole nizbrdo?

194
00:22:12,364 --> 00:22:13,991
Da.

195
00:22:14,099 --> 00:22:17,034
Hej! Nemoj to da radis.
Ubices se.

196
00:22:45,364 --> 00:22:49,733
- Da li ga je pregledao vojni lekar.?
- Vojni lekar je rekao da nema potrebe za lecenjem, gospodine.

197
00:22:49,835 --> 00:22:51,769
Zatvorenik i pratnja...

198
00:22:51,870 --> 00:22:54,964
i... okret!

199
00:22:56,942 --> 00:22:59,968
Zatvorenik i pratnja, brzi mars!

200
00:23:00,078 --> 00:23:02,638
Leva, desna! Leva, desna!

201
00:23:02,748 --> 00:23:04,716
Zatvorenik i pratnja, stoj!

202
00:24:20,292 --> 00:24:22,487
Redove Bedous, ulazi!

203
00:24:27,466 --> 00:24:30,924
U 0900 casova, vi cete paradno
proci kroz glavnu kapiju...

204
00:24:31,036 --> 00:24:34,005
gde cete sacekati transport
koji ce vas odvesti u vase jedinice.

205
00:24:34,105 --> 00:24:36,232
Vraticete se ovde do 2100 sati...

206
00:24:36,341 --> 00:24:39,606
ili vas rodjena majka nece prepoznati
kad ja budem zavrsio sa vama.

207
00:24:39,711 --> 00:24:42,271
Zaboravite sve sto sam vam rekao
i nece vas biti u blizini...

208
00:24:42,380 --> 00:24:45,178
- Utesno, zar ne?
- ...da mi napisete pismo zahvalnosti
kada se rat bude zavrsio.

209
00:24:45,283 --> 00:24:48,081
Saljes signale, Bedous?

210
00:24:48,186 --> 00:24:50,347
Samo za "pobedu," kaplare.

211
00:24:54,092 --> 00:24:55,992
Ovo je Muviton.

212
00:32:04,222 --> 00:32:06,156
Lezi dole tamo! Lezi dole!

213
00:32:53,304 --> 00:32:55,864
- Zdravo, Dzek.
- Sve moramo sami, zar ne?

214
00:33:02,880 --> 00:33:05,041
Ti si usamljenicka vrsta
